plot: A chronicle of the heavy metal band Pantera's 1992 tour, behind the &"Vulgar Display of Power&" album, that chronicles all of the band's excesses with groupies, drinking and drugs. Also featured in the video are members of White Zombie, Megadeth and Metallica.   Written by  Anonymous
title: Pantera Vulgar Video
